{"tid":581952,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好好珍惜時間，有一日你會發現時間真係過得快","createTime":"2018-03-05T18:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T18:37:37.000Z","uid":2004,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4619311f42cf085890302d413f14f680554d4c98","tid":581952,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"做做下嘢，無端端有一種好可惜嘅感覺，可惜一啲以前荒廢咗嘅時間，係正確嘅時間冇做正確嘅事。中學畢業到依家仲讀緊書，一諗起讀埋出年就要投身呢個社會，心情有啲複雜。<br />\n<br />\n細個會想快啲大個，想好自由咁去做自己鍾意嘅事，覺得讀書嘅日子好苦悶，中學嘅時候仲天真咁覺得不如直接出黎做嘢搵錢好過，自己搵錢自己使。<br />\n<br />\n直到依家雖然仲讀緊書，但係感覺唔同中學嘅時候，所有嘢都好chur，chur到你已經feel到同返緊工冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n打緊呢篇嘢嘅時候我仲忙緊啲功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中學嘅日子雖然冇乜特別，渾渾噩噩咁就過咗6年，講真DSE相比起依家黎講真係冇咁大壓力，倒不如諗下日後嘅生活點算仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗若你同我一樣有一日突然覺得時間過得好快，你已經唔係一個on99咁過日子嘅細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係懷念中學同班fd on99嘅日子，彈女同學bra帶，同曖昧對象係學校一齊行俾班fd周圍大聲唱但又幫我去溝條女嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6682809e1ffcaa3590f1870e429c1106d0669c6d","tid":581952,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"啱 中學戇戇鳩鳩就過咗六年<br />\n<br />\n大個咗先知到中學嘅時候係最好"},{"pid":"17d42725bff30ef367874fc2e508df0da87aa5fa","tid":581952,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"我終於長大了 很開心喔哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f689053565d472949d2be2355570d7de0e949f52","tid":581952,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116f70641660876b40269de3e222f0f4410c4c5e","tid":581952,"uid":171410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"做功課啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2ac861927040c0cc23326803946336c58e54a4","tid":581952,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6682809e1ffcaa3590f1870e429c1106d0669c6d","tid":581952,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"啱 中學戇戇鳩鳩就過咗六年<br />\n<br />\n大個咗先知到中學嘅時候係最好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"雖然識好多豬朋狗友，但都會有幾位知己良朋。<br />\n慶幸自己雖然讀Band3學校，但係都有好多好老師，真心當我呢班學生係朋友，放學一齊打波，閒日出黎食宵夜嘅老師，好彩冇經歷教畜嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27b1a3b717a72f15ba678c82de6b2ca0d84e025","tid":581952,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"116f70641660876b40269de3e222f0f4410c4c5e","tid":581952,"uid":171410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"做功課啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己友唔洗咁嘅。"},{"pid":"439d726482f3a11e9931c56bcd1e026282dddff0","tid":581952,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17d42725bff30ef367874fc2e508df0da87aa5fa","tid":581952,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"我終於長大了 很開心喔哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"唔知你認真定假膠，唔好再浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9e2024fc6a230218d5f6aa571cd49601360325","tid":581952,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e2ac861927040c0cc23326803946336c58e54a4","tid":581952,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6682809e1ffcaa3590f1870e429c1106d0669c6d","tid":581952,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20